544
00:29:31,240 --> 00:29:35,129
To the extent that Frank's
brought out the mother in me, yes.

545
00:29:35,328 --> 00:29:37,590
I'd like some coffee.

546
00:29:38,247 --> 00:29:41,374
And I'd like to get to know
Mr. Dodd better.

547
00:29:41,375 --> 00:29:43,512
I'd like to get to know you better.

548
00:29:44,420 --> 00:29:46,599
Shall we go along?

549
00:29:49,091 --> 00:29:50,353
Yes.

550
00:29:50,968 --> 00:29:53,105
The theater's mysterious.

551
