It sure is.

552
00:30:13,616 --> 00:30:15,336
This way, please.

553
00:30:22,959 --> 00:30:24,595
Hi, Charlie.

554
00:30:24,794 --> 00:30:26,972
Excuse me a minute, will you, honey?

555
00:30:27,797 --> 00:30:29,934
No, thanks, never use them.

556
00:30:31,550 --> 00:30:34,146
Are you really satisfied
with Frank's work, Mr. Dodd?

557
00:30:35,179 --> 00:30:37,889
I'll be happy
when he gets the part out of his hands.

558
00:30:37,890 --> 00:30:40,361
He has his worries with those lines.

559
00:30:41,477 --> 00:30:44,646
And I'd appreciate it if you didn't
add to those worries, Mrs. Elgin.

560
00:30:44,647 --> 00:30:46,314
He seems to be more concerned about

561
00:30:46,315 --> 00:30:49,161
