his performance than the audience.

562
00:30:49,568 --> 00:30:52,623
You mean he's too focused
on my reaction?

563
00:30:53,406 --> 00:30:55,532
That's one way of putting it.

564
00:30:55,533 --> 00:30:59,296
You could help a lot
by being careful of what you do and say.

565
00:31:00,454 --> 00:31:03,540
I try to be careful, Mr. Dodd,
but being an actor's wife

566
00:31:03,541 --> 00:31:05,709
