00:31:41,412 --> 00:31:44,341
That still doesn't prove
her theory was completely wrong.

580
00:31:45,374 --> 00:31:48,762
I imagine one could go through history
and find a few good examples.

581
00:31:49,378 --> 00:31:53,225
It's a pity that Leonardo da Vinci
never had a wife to guide him.

582
00:31:53,591 --> 00:31:55,352
He might've really gotten somewhere.

